      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Citadel Security",
        "Client": "Man with a Calm Air",
        "Description": "A rascal in my family knocked\r\nover our ancestral offering. The\r\nfruit is native to the highlands\r\nof the Citadel, but the trouble\r\nof growing them keeps it off the\r\nmarket. I require an escort to\r\ngo pick some myself.",
